WEBVTT

00:22.564 --> 00:24.649
- Up on your end.
- Back this way.

00:24.817 --> 00:26.943
Keep in line.

00:27.111 --> 00:29.696
Mommy, help me!

00:31.448 --> 00:34.033
Can't catch me.

00:35.202 --> 00:37.203
This way.

01:01.895 --> 01:04.021
Net and trident?

01:04.188 --> 01:07.066
The man appears more common
fisherman than gladiator.

01:07.234 --> 01:10.778
The style is called retiarius,
carried from the outer regions.

01:10.946 --> 01:13.197
They should carry it back.
I favor the murmillo.

01:18.203 --> 01:20.246
The crowd is of the opposite opinion.

01:28.046 --> 01:30.089
Aah!

01:35.012 --> 01:39.348
Soon there will be a retiarius
in the sands in every game.

01:39.516 --> 01:42.894
And the Ludus absent them
tragically lacking.

01:43.061 --> 01:44.479
Very well.

01:44.646 --> 01:47.732
Yet place net and trident in the hands
of one of our lesser men.

01:54.865 --> 01:55.865
Oh!

02:16.720 --> 02:18.679
Did I not tell you?
Listen to them.

02:18.847 --> 02:20.223
A spectacle to be sure.

02:20.390 --> 02:23.810
All the more thrilling if viewed
from the pulvinus.

02:23.977 --> 02:27.396
- Invitation was extended.
- And refused?

02:27.564 --> 02:29.440
The pulvinus is too far removed.

02:29.608 --> 02:31.859
I would witness the games here
among the people

02:32.027 --> 02:34.946
with son beside me.

02:45.833 --> 02:47.542
Your hour is upon you.

02:53.131 --> 02:55.174
A fine blade.

02:56.176 --> 02:58.594
To be wielded with deadly purpose.

02:58.762 --> 03:02.056
Reform my words in manner
Dagan understands.

03:03.392 --> 03:05.518
You bear the mark
of the brotherhood.

03:07.271 --> 03:10.189
An honor you have not earned.

03:10.357 --> 03:13.651
Your true test awaits you.

03:13.819 --> 03:16.529
Live and count yourself
among us.

03:17.698 --> 03:22.076
Die and prove yourselves
as unworthy as I suspect.

03:28.876 --> 03:32.879
Dagan says he will honor the House
of Batiatus with gifts of blood.

03:33.964 --> 03:36.299
As will the mighty Ashur.

03:36.466 --> 03:38.968
Then do not die too quickly.

03:56.445 --> 03:58.195
Go on, Ashur!

04:08.957 --> 04:10.791
Come on. Yes!

04:20.510 --> 04:22.011
Yes!

04:37.235 --> 04:39.278
Come on!

04:39.446 --> 04:42.073
No!

04:45.202 --> 04:46.869
Fucking yes!

04:49.373 --> 04:51.958
Show them no mercy!

05:06.682 --> 05:08.599
Yes!

05:12.104 --> 05:14.522
Hasdrubal falls!

05:14.690 --> 05:18.859
As all men who face Ashur!

05:19.027 --> 05:21.779
The man assumes credit
owed his betters.

05:21.947 --> 05:24.198
He is but swollen by the moment.

05:24.366 --> 05:27.326
Perhaps he will turn
greater performance next time.

05:28.412 --> 05:30.705
You speak of what
may never pass.

05:32.499 --> 05:34.583
Now the lesser matches
have passed,

05:34.751 --> 05:37.253
let us see something of note.

05:37.421 --> 05:40.589
Vettius, make presentation.

05:40.757 --> 05:43.634
I give the good people
of Capua this day

05:43.802 --> 05:45.803
my latest acquisition,

05:45.971 --> 05:48.055
certain to inflame passion

05:48.223 --> 05:50.891
and ignite fear in all who oppose him.

05:51.059 --> 05:53.644
From the darkest lands
east of the Rhine,

05:53.812 --> 05:57.857
behold Caburus Murmillo.

06:04.239 --> 06:06.699
The crowd favors Vettius' offering.

06:06.867 --> 06:10.870
They greet Gannicus with louder voice,
yet he stands removed from the games.

06:11.038 --> 06:13.622
Enter Drappes Thraex.

06:15.250 --> 06:18.085
Crixus shows promise,
yet again the same fate.

06:18.253 --> 06:20.796
Our men see victory
only to be awarded exclusion.

06:20.964 --> 06:24.592
The fruits reaped when you offend a man
beyond our station.

06:24.760 --> 06:26.260
Begin.

06:30.974 --> 06:34.435
I but stood ground to protect
our house as any Lanista would.

06:34.603 --> 06:37.897
Yet ambition beyond the title
clouds your judgment.

06:40.233 --> 06:43.694
We must be humble
if I am to repair relations

06:43.862 --> 06:45.780
with Tullius and see all our
men returned to the sands.

06:45.947 --> 06:47.907
Quickly I pray if we are
to place our men

06:48.075 --> 06:49.617
in the opening games
of the new arena.

06:49.785 --> 06:52.265
Reaching for such heights is what
sent you tumbling from favor.

06:53.789 --> 06:56.290
Strike it from your thoughts.

06:56.458 --> 06:59.460
Place mind and effort towards
more reasonable pursuits.

07:00.462 --> 07:04.298
Caburus! Caburus!

07:04.466 --> 07:08.427
Perhaps the procuring of a man
as worthy as Caburus.

07:12.099 --> 07:14.767
Fleeting opportunity
to enjoy the old arena

07:14.935 --> 07:18.270
and yet we're swept aside,
absent even casual regard.

07:18.438 --> 07:20.314
I consider it a blessing

07:20.482 --> 07:22.942
to be so reprieved
from condemning presence.

07:23.110 --> 07:26.445
The manner Titus glares at us, it is
a shock we do not burst into flame.

07:26.613 --> 07:29.615
He is but an old man
set upon his ways.

07:29.783 --> 07:33.035
He is a gorgon with a cock
turning all around him to stone.

07:33.203 --> 07:37.123
Titus does not fare well
in the dust and the heat.

07:37.290 --> 07:41.168
His health will prompt return
to the coast of Sicilia very soon.

07:41.336 --> 07:45.339
Until such glorious event, I would fade
from beneath his oppressive roof.

07:46.550 --> 07:48.467
You would leave me?

07:50.137 --> 07:53.180
You are with husband.

07:53.348 --> 07:57.101
A man who would never see you
harmed by whim or circumstance.

07:58.270 --> 07:59.937
I stand alone,

08:00.105 --> 08:02.857
severed from such protection.

08:03.024 --> 08:06.277
A perilous condition
that must be attended.

08:06.444 --> 08:09.822
You are never alone
while I draw breath.

08:11.783 --> 08:13.993
Words of much comfort.

08:15.328 --> 08:17.997
Though a husband with heavy purse
would be more so.

08:18.165 --> 08:21.041
Then we must find one
suitable to cause.

08:22.169 --> 08:25.629
A possibility presents itself
in most pleasing form.

08:25.797 --> 08:27.923
You know the man?

08:28.091 --> 08:31.177
I've seen him about in Rome
absent encumbrance of a wife.

08:31.344 --> 08:35.306
Well, how fortunate that we should come
upon him at this time and place.

08:37.225 --> 08:40.519
In desperate times fortune must
give way to more assertive hands.

08:44.316 --> 08:46.692
Petronius.

08:46.860 --> 08:50.112
Would the gods have me so blessed?

08:51.823 --> 08:54.700
Gaia. We were introduced
at one of Varus's affairs.

08:54.868 --> 08:56.994
Oh yes.

08:57.162 --> 08:59.997
- Yes yes, of course. Apologies.
- None required.

09:00.165 --> 09:02.833
Seeing you so unexpected
has lifted questionable spirits.

09:03.001 --> 09:04.627
Oh.

09:04.794 --> 09:07.129
- Lucretia can attest...
- You're Lucretia?

09:07.297 --> 09:10.925
Wife to the Lanista Batiatus?

09:11.092 --> 09:13.260
I do call him husband, yes.

09:13.428 --> 09:17.139
I have heard
your house spoken of

09:17.307 --> 09:20.851
and the, um, pleasures
contained within.

09:46.795 --> 09:49.296
Barca has lost form
since Auctus fell.

09:49.464 --> 09:51.215
His cock will find
another hole to fuck.

09:53.260 --> 09:57.554
Ah, we return anointed
in the blood

09:57.722 --> 09:59.390
of our enemies.

09:59.557 --> 10:01.642
Hasdrubal and Kleitos
met their end.

10:01.810 --> 10:05.312
The first of many to fall
beneath our swords in the arena.

10:07.691 --> 10:10.150
See yourselves to the baths.

10:14.572 --> 10:17.074
Gannicus. Pair with Rhaskos.

10:17.242 --> 10:18.784
To what end?

10:18.952 --> 10:21.620
If I am not to fight in the arena
I'll remain here in the shade.

10:21.788 --> 10:24.623
Doctore.

10:24.791 --> 10:28.377
Send the man up.
I would have words.

10:29.713 --> 10:31.839
Magnetius.

10:32.007 --> 10:34.550
One of the finest champions
this house has ever forged.

10:38.555 --> 10:40.347
He stood a titan.

10:40.515 --> 10:42.641
As all my champions.

10:42.809 --> 10:45.352
The culmination
of years of training,

10:45.520 --> 10:48.022
dedication, sacrifice.

10:52.569 --> 10:55.029
You would hold
yourself their equal?

10:55.196 --> 10:57.406
In the arena
I am every man's equal.

10:57.574 --> 10:59.867
Hmm.

11:00.035 --> 11:03.495
The champion is more than
his victories upon the sands.

11:06.207 --> 11:08.083
He is the sum of his actions.

11:08.251 --> 11:11.170
Every decision, no matter how small,
speaks to the man

11:11.338 --> 11:13.088
in the balance of his heart.

11:13.256 --> 11:15.632
In his breast beats the heart of a lion.

11:19.471 --> 11:21.889
And what does it beat for?

11:22.057 --> 11:25.100
The House of Batiatus.

11:30.106 --> 11:32.066
Return him to the Ludus.

11:36.071 --> 11:39.531
See? The man fights for the honor
of this house

11:39.699 --> 11:41.219
as all your champions
have in the past.

11:41.368 --> 11:45.204
Gannicus speaks but words
he knows I seek to hear.

11:45.372 --> 11:48.665
He is no champion of my house.

11:54.130 --> 11:56.799
I stand before Petronius
with obvious charms

11:56.966 --> 12:00.094
and all he can do is prattle
about the House of Batiatus.

12:01.388 --> 12:03.722
I fear I've lost delicate touch.

12:03.890 --> 12:06.934
Your touch is many things,
delicate not among them.

12:07.936 --> 12:09.144
You're of a mood.

12:09.312 --> 12:12.773
If word of what we have offered
has spread to Petronius,

12:12.941 --> 12:14.942
how long before it lights
on Titus' ear?

12:15.110 --> 12:17.027
Perhaps it should.

12:17.195 --> 12:18.862
The shock would no doubt
end the old goat.

12:19.030 --> 12:21.949
You jest while all around us
threatens to fucking crumble.

12:22.117 --> 12:24.952
The only threat is of you and Quintus
becoming favored among the elite.

12:25.120 --> 12:27.746
As a whore is favored
by the man atop her.

12:27.914 --> 12:31.125
It is not as if all of Rome knows.

12:32.877 --> 12:34.920
Only the most privileged tongues

12:35.088 --> 12:37.714
whisper of the delights
offered within these walls.

12:37.882 --> 12:42.010
Delights Petronius and his friends
long to witness for themselves.

12:42.178 --> 12:45.639
To even consider it
is beyond reason.

12:45.807 --> 12:47.766
If Titus were to...

12:47.934 --> 12:50.102
What joys does my father
prevent now?

12:51.521 --> 12:54.231
None of note.

12:57.110 --> 12:59.862
We came across Petronius
in the market.

13:00.029 --> 13:01.780
You are familiar with the name?

13:01.948 --> 13:05.284
As any man with their mind towards
business and the procuring of it.

13:05.452 --> 13:07.932
He is familiar with yours as well
and spoke with great interest

13:08.037 --> 13:10.539
of sampling of your more
exotic offerings

13:10.707 --> 13:13.500
with acquaintances
of equal position.

13:13.668 --> 13:16.003
And how did good Petronius
come to hear of such things?

13:16.171 --> 13:18.213
Varus and Cossutius.

13:18.381 --> 13:20.507
Their tongues are looser
than their cocks.

13:20.675 --> 13:22.801
Petronius departs for Rome
the day after next.

13:22.969 --> 13:26.597
Decision must be given quick birth
or see opportunity aborted.

13:28.391 --> 13:30.767
With the support of Petronius
we may yet find position

13:30.935 --> 13:32.519
in the opening games
of the new arena.

13:32.687 --> 13:34.354
- Quintus, your father...
- Make the arrangements.

13:34.522 --> 13:35.981
I'll attend to my father.

13:55.460 --> 13:58.378
Melitta. A word.

13:58.546 --> 13:59.922
I have none to give.

14:00.089 --> 14:02.633
It is a matter of some importance.

14:03.635 --> 14:05.010
A moment.

14:12.101 --> 14:14.186
You avoid my gaze.

14:14.354 --> 14:18.732
As you should mine
lest suspicions be aroused.

14:18.900 --> 14:20.984
Should they not also be aroused

14:21.152 --> 14:24.238
if two friends are no longer
seen to speak?

14:24.405 --> 14:26.865
What happened between us...

14:27.033 --> 14:28.784
Was not of our choosing.

14:28.952 --> 14:32.579
We must turn it from thought
and never give it voice.

14:32.747 --> 14:36.500
My tongue, it bends
to such warning.

14:37.585 --> 14:39.711
Yet the thought of you,

14:39.879 --> 14:41.964
it proves troublesome.

14:42.131 --> 14:45.050
The memory will fade with time,

14:45.218 --> 14:47.469
as do all things born
of misfortune.

14:51.724 --> 14:54.851
We were as brothers once
but no more.

14:56.813 --> 14:59.982
The men no longer accept me
as a gladiator

15:00.149 --> 15:02.901
and do not yet give respect
as doctore.

15:03.069 --> 15:06.822
Even Gannicus refuses
to heed my instruction.

15:08.950 --> 15:12.536
Gannicus heeds nothing
but his own desires

15:12.704 --> 15:14.913
beyond all reason.

15:15.081 --> 15:19.835
You must teach him that you alone
are in command.

15:20.003 --> 15:24.089
And by firm hand erase all doubts.

15:26.301 --> 15:29.511
Show them all the man
that I've given my heart to.

16:10.136 --> 16:11.845
Gnaeus.

16:12.013 --> 16:14.431
Your mastery of the sword
falls to question.

16:14.599 --> 16:17.184
The net and trident
are your weapons now.

16:17.352 --> 16:19.853
A fucking net, Oenomaus?

16:32.617 --> 16:35.911
You will do as commanded
absent complaint

16:36.079 --> 16:38.664
or see flesh stripped from bone.

16:40.375 --> 16:42.626
Yes, Doctore.

16:46.464 --> 16:48.674
Return to training.

16:51.761 --> 16:53.929
You speak as Jupiter hurling bolts
from the heavens.

16:54.097 --> 16:57.808
Raised there by words
and touch of loving wife.

16:59.018 --> 17:03.689
Now pair with Barca
and remain far from the shade.

17:11.155 --> 17:14.825
Barca.
Bring fucking spear to purpose.

17:17.078 --> 17:18.369
Again.

17:23.041 --> 17:25.794
Your man shows fire today.

17:25.962 --> 17:27.963
Ignited by your words I'm sure.

17:30.383 --> 17:32.801
- Honeyed wine, quickly.
- I'm fine.

17:32.969 --> 17:35.637
Sound and pallor
threaten disagreement.

17:35.805 --> 17:38.765
You are too long
from the salt air of the coast.

17:38.933 --> 17:40.934
And shall remain
from Sicilia longer still.

17:41.102 --> 17:44.187
- Do not waste breath on the matter.
- I would not see you so far removed.

17:44.355 --> 17:46.982
But a day or more
by the waters of Neapolis?

17:47.150 --> 17:48.859
- Oh.
- Yes, to revive color.

17:50.778 --> 17:53.947
My concern lies only
with this Ludus

17:54.115 --> 17:56.074
and seeing it to former glories.

17:56.242 --> 17:58.452
Well, then let our journey
serve dual cause.

17:58.619 --> 18:01.079
We can review the latest
shipment of slaves

18:01.247 --> 18:04.374
with mind towards procuring
a champion favored by us both.

18:04.542 --> 18:06.418
Someone to rival
Vettius' new man.

18:09.505 --> 18:11.506
Drink.

18:18.514 --> 18:22.058
You conspire against an old man.

18:24.145 --> 18:27.355
To your advantage.
Make preparation.

18:27.523 --> 18:29.983
We leave for Neapolis.

18:31.903 --> 18:34.070
See to my father.

18:37.158 --> 18:38.825
He is attended to as promised.

18:38.993 --> 18:41.703
Have Gaia send word to Petronius.
You entertain tonight.

18:41.871 --> 18:44.080
If he and his circle overreach?

18:44.248 --> 18:47.709
The appetites of men are not easily
set aside by the words of a woman.

18:47.877 --> 18:49.586
We'll send message to Solonius.

18:49.754 --> 18:52.074
He can stand in my place,
speak for the house if so needed.

18:52.131 --> 18:55.133
- Quintus.
- The risk outweighs concern.

18:55.301 --> 18:57.594
See to Petronius and his guests.

18:57.762 --> 19:01.348
And with their satisfaction our position
in the opening games is secured.

19:13.653 --> 19:16.071
Snare any fish today
in your little net?

19:19.492 --> 19:21.451
Reward for victory in the arena.

19:21.619 --> 19:24.704
Continue and see more weigh palm.

19:28.668 --> 19:31.336
Dagan questions receiving
the greater sum.

19:31.504 --> 19:33.880
We stood equally upon the sands.

19:34.048 --> 19:36.758
Tell him he receives twice the coin

19:36.926 --> 19:38.385
because you are half the man.

19:39.720 --> 19:44.057
I am a gladiator as he is.

19:44.225 --> 19:47.477
If we did not need you to exchange
our words for his,

19:47.645 --> 19:51.356
you would never have been given
chance to take up sword.

20:10.585 --> 20:13.712
Bread for your pets.

20:21.846 --> 20:25.974
Doiros was the brother
I held closest to me.

20:26.142 --> 20:28.894
He was a fierce warrior,

20:29.061 --> 20:31.271
as was my father
and all before us.

20:31.439 --> 20:35.692
I would sit at their feet and listen
to their many stories of battle,

20:35.860 --> 20:38.194
longing for the day
when I could pick up arms

20:38.362 --> 20:40.113
and stand beside them in glory.

20:40.281 --> 20:43.366
My father, my brothers,

20:43.534 --> 20:47.704
Doiros... I watched as they all fell
beneath the spears of the Arverni.

20:49.916 --> 20:52.459
My hand yet too small
to pick up sword,

20:52.627 --> 20:56.755
I was forced to serve,
to bow and scrape.

20:56.923 --> 20:59.215
First of all to the shits
who took my family

20:59.383 --> 21:02.260
and then to the Romans
they sold me to.

21:02.428 --> 21:07.057
Not a day passes where I do not dream
of honoring the dead,

21:07.224 --> 21:10.060
of proving myself worthy to them

21:10.227 --> 21:12.771
in blood and victory.

21:12.939 --> 21:16.399
Auctus is the first life
I've ever taken in battle.

21:19.070 --> 21:21.029
He will not be forgotten.

21:24.241 --> 21:25.951
They were Auctus' pets.

21:28.329 --> 21:31.164
I never favored them.

21:36.379 --> 21:38.755
Now they are all that's left.

21:54.605 --> 21:56.940
Line 'em up.
Make 'em stand up straight.

21:59.026 --> 22:00.402
What of this one?

22:00.569 --> 22:03.947
See how his form is carved with each
muscle building on to the next?

22:04.115 --> 22:06.658
A worthy addition to any Ludus.

22:07.660 --> 22:09.369
A fine offering, is he not?

22:09.537 --> 22:11.121
I would not waste coin.

22:11.288 --> 22:14.290
The man favors his left
revealing injury to the leg.

22:14.458 --> 22:17.544
Unsuitable for men of discerning eye.

22:17.712 --> 22:21.339
Let us turn to something
of rarer quality.

22:21.507 --> 22:25.343
I have a Thracian of the Maedi tribe,

22:25.511 --> 22:27.387
the likes of which you have...

22:27.555 --> 22:30.682
Thracians are too difficult to control
and aggravate the Gauls beyond reason.

22:30.850 --> 22:33.059
My son speaks truth.

22:33.227 --> 22:36.688
You offer us piss
and claim it wine.

22:36.856 --> 22:39.024
You'll find none better in Neapolis.

22:39.191 --> 22:41.943
I would hope your city's drink
holds higher standard.

22:42.111 --> 22:44.362
Come, let us seek libation

22:44.530 --> 22:46.698
to wash the taste of shit
from mouth.

22:59.253 --> 23:01.546
- Diona.
- It does not hurt.

23:01.714 --> 23:05.925
Wait. We haven't spoken
or laughed as we usually do.

23:06.093 --> 23:07.927
I have no time for childish things.

23:09.138 --> 23:12.182
Domina wishes me bathed
for tonight.

23:15.811 --> 23:18.104
Take this to Oenomaus. These men
are to be brought to the villa

23:18.272 --> 23:20.774
- properly oiled and scented.
- Yes, Domina.

23:20.941 --> 23:24.611
There is much I will need
attended to tonight.

23:24.779 --> 23:26.988
I would have you by my side,

23:27.156 --> 23:29.824
not be dislodged by any request.

23:29.992 --> 23:31.743
Gratitude.

23:31.911 --> 23:36.414
There is one thing
that I would ask you in return.

23:38.000 --> 23:41.336
It is well known that your husband's
allegiance lies with Titus.

23:41.504 --> 23:44.964
Sway him to keep what we do here
confined to shadow,

23:45.132 --> 23:48.051
or I fear that other secrets

23:48.219 --> 23:49.803
will find their way into the light.

23:52.681 --> 23:54.015
Am I understood?

23:54.183 --> 23:56.309
Yes, Domina.

23:56.477 --> 23:58.228
See it done.

24:10.116 --> 24:12.158
Venus blushes in her garden,

24:12.326 --> 24:14.577
shamed by such beauty.

24:14.745 --> 24:18.665
Would that she stood in my place
and I among the roots and leaves.

24:20.167 --> 24:23.294
These hands were not meant
for common earth.

24:23.462 --> 24:26.506
They have held me close
as dearest friend,

24:26.674 --> 24:28.466
as sister.

24:30.052 --> 24:32.303
Tonight mine shall return favor

24:32.471 --> 24:36.349
and aid yours in seizing position
so richly deserved.

24:37.726 --> 24:40.061
