stand erect with expectation.

30:27.951 --> 30:30.870
Let us see them to climax.

30:31.038 --> 30:32.955
Bring them in.

30:42.633 --> 30:46.469
Good Tullius, seeing you here
comes as surprise.

30:46.637 --> 30:49.388
