that it would bring.

31:01.276 --> 31:04.612
You warned me to grow favor.

31:05.906 --> 31:08.574
Continue speaking
and see it wither.

31:18.043 --> 31:21.212
You have shared drink, food,

31:21.380 --> 31:25.174
distractions of the eye and ear.

31:25.342 --> 31:28.678
Yet these are common things
enjoyed by men

31:28.845 --> 31:31.931
