from such human constraints.

31:37.563 --> 31:40.356
Touch these to flesh.

31:40.524 --> 31:42.984
Sever all ties from the mortal world

31:43.151 --> 31:47.446
and rise as gods
in the House of Batiatus.

31:51.910 --> 31:54.120
Oh, Jupiter.

31:54.288 --> 31:57.123
Never in our dealings, Tullius,

31:57.291 --> 31:59.917
have I been so elevated.

32:00.085 --> 32:02.920
This house truly is a marvel.

32:04.089 --> 32:07.925
