32:24.109 --> 32:25.401
Wood?

32:25.569 --> 32:29.989
But the clash of steel rings through
the halls of Olympus, does it not?

32:31.533 --> 32:33.326
Give them your swords.

32:33.493 --> 32:35.828
Let us clear space and have contest.

32:43.086 --> 32:45.421
See grin removed.

32:45.589 --> 32:48.507
You are to indulge him,
allow a show of blood.

32:48.675 --> 32:51.594
But level no insult
nor injury in return.

32:51.762 --> 32:54.513
