34:02.958 --> 34:05.668
I stand unscathed.

34:05.836 --> 34:08.420
Perhaps you are not
the champion I believed.

34:08.588 --> 34:10.464
This goes too far.

34:45.333 --> 34:47.460
Tullius!

34:47.627 --> 34:50.838
