36:00.158 --> 36:02.868
I should return to the villa.

36:03.036 --> 36:04.578
You should.

36:05.747 --> 36:08.874
Why are you doing this?

36:09.042 --> 36:10.960
Because to not would be a lie

36:11.127 --> 36:13.128
much deeper than the one
we tell Oenomaus.

36:13.296 --> 36:15.923
I did not want this.

36:16.091 --> 36:19.218
I love that man like a brother.

36:20.345 --> 36:22.096
Yet what I feel for you...

36:24.474 --> 36:27.685
Tell me it does not stir
in your breast as well.

36:27.853 --> 36:29.353
What I feel means nothing.

36:29.521 --> 36:31.355
It holds the world.

36:31.523 --> 36:34.733
What would you do if you were my husband
and you learned of such a thing?

36:34.901 --> 36:36.694
I would kill us both.

37:28.121 --> 37:30.623
You are an imposing brute.

37:30.790 --> 37:34.376
Tell me, giant,
where do your tastes lie?

37:34.544 --> 37:37.087
Toward cock or cunt?

37:37.255 --> 37:40.257
Uh, apologies.
He does not grasp your language.

37:40.425 --> 37:42.760
Are you able to form words
so that he may?

37:47.098 --> 37:48.849
