37:49.017 --> 37:53.187
I do not care
for struggle nor complaint.

37:53.355 --> 37:55.481
Will you submit to all I ask for?

38:05.283 --> 38:07.826
- He's agreeable.
- Come then.

38:07.994 --> 38:09.745
I'll have your ass quickly.

38:16.753 --> 38:19.296
