of a gentle nature.

38:19.464 --> 38:22.299
A brute such as this
craves rough hands

38:22.467 --> 38:24.510
and cock their equal.

38:24.678 --> 38:27.429
Then he shall be well satisfied.
Come.

38:37.649 --> 38:39.400
How does he fare?

38:39.567 --> 38:41.151
Painfully, yet he lives.

38:41.319 --> 38:42.987
It should not have happened.

38:43.154 --> 38:45.030
To be said
of many things this night.

38:52.706 --> 38:54.957
He does not drink,
he does not fuck.

38:55.125 --> 38:58.127
- Why does he remain?
- The man is a mystery.

38:58.294 --> 39:02.256
One I would have forever solved.
You could gauge nothing of his intent?

39:02.424 --> 39:04.675
He fears your husband
attempts maneuver.

39:04.843 --> 39:07.970
I believe his presence is meant
only to rattle nerves.

39:11.182 --> 39:14.768
Tullius will give voice of this
until the din reaches Titus's ears.

39:14.936 --> 39:17.896
Then we must keep
his tongue occupied.

39:18.064 --> 39:20.524
You believe your charms
will sway him?

39:20.692 --> 39:22.609
You know nothing of women, Solonius.

39:22.777 --> 39:26.030
And even less of their charms.

39:27.407 --> 39:29.783
Oh, I would not ask you to do this.

39:29.951 --> 39:32.619
- That is why I offer.
- The only reason?

39:32.787 --> 39:35.372
The man proves troublesome thorn.

39:35.540 --> 39:37.624
Who better to remove it
than trusted friend?

39:37.792 --> 39:38.959
Gaia...

39:39.127 --> 39:41.503
Keep thoughts
towards elevating this house.

39:41.671 --> 39:43.589
I will see to Tullius.

39:43.757 --> 39:46.717
And in the act secure
elevation of my own

39:46.885 --> 39:49.219
to the benefit of all.

39:55.602 --> 39:58.562
The woman thinks highly of herself.

39:58.730 --> 40:02.316
An estimation deeply shared.

40:02.484 --> 40:05.736
You've become a difficult man
to gain private audience with.

40:05.904 --> 40:09.114
It was not always so.

40:10.408 --> 40:12.868
Much has changed
since our youth.

40:15.997 --> 40:17.706
Not everything, I hope.

40:20.210 --> 40:22.753
I remember a time when it was you

40:22.921 --> 40:25.422
who was impossible to trap alone.

40:26.674 --> 40:29.426
Every man in Capua was at your feet.

40:31.763 --> 40:34.848
Now I would have but one

40:35.016 --> 40:37.434
standing beside me.

40:46.903 --> 40:50.447
I was saddened to hear
of your husband's passing.

40:50.615 --> 40:52.991
Were you?

40:56.788 --> 40:58.664
Only with thoughts toward you

40:58.832 --> 41:02.000
