with no family to speak of.

41:03.628 --> 41:05.504
No one to care for you.

41:08.633 --> 41:11.135
It is a difficult thing

41:11.302 --> 41:14.138
to find a man of my standing.

41:18.143 --> 41:20.561
I always favored this color.

41:23.064 --> 41:24.773
I know.

41:26.860 --> 41:29.278
The gods smile upon me

41:29.445 --> 41:32.406
having had word
of this night reach my ears.

41:32.574 --> 41:34.158
The fortune is mine.

41:34.325 --> 41:37.494
Yet I would have word of it
travel no further.

41:42.333 --> 41:45.043
You petition this for yourself?

41:48.047 --> 41:51.466
Or for the House of Batiatus?

41:53.678 --> 41:56.263
Lucretia is as a sister to me.

41:56.431 --> 41:58.849
Mmm.

41:59.017 --> 42:02.269
I would not see her injured
by wagging tongue.

42:03.730 --> 42:06.690
You ask much.

42:06.858 --> 42:08.775
I offer more.

42:22.290 --> 42:25.375
I swear never to speak of what
has happened this night...

42:26.753 --> 42:29.755
if you would deliver
a message to your friend...

42:31.216 --> 42:33.008
and her husband.

42:33.176 --> 42:35.552
One they would take to heart...

42:37.972 --> 42:39.348
coming from you.

43:01.079 --> 43:04.081
Words have not inflated beyond truth.

43:04.249 --> 43:08.961
The offerings of the House of Batiatus
are truly to be admired.

43:09.128 --> 43:12.339
Well, even more so upon the sands.

43:12.507 --> 43:15.217
Imagine the excitement
our wares would cause

43:15.385 --> 43:18.178
if included in the opening celebration
of the new arena.

43:18.346 --> 43:21.181
Capua would be blessed
by such appearance.

43:21.349 --> 43:24.017
I'll send word to your husband
to discuss the matter.

43:29.941 --> 43:33.068
Oh, I thought this night
would never end.

43:33.236 --> 43:37.114
It concludes with this house
soaring to the heavens upon your wings.

43:37.282 --> 43:39.700
A feat aided by your presence.

43:39.867 --> 43:42.244
The evening would have gone
as well had I never known.

43:42.412 --> 43:43.620
Perhaps more so.

43:44.956 --> 43:46.999
The hour is late.

43:47.166 --> 43:50.085
Take to your bed
and carry with you my gratitude.

43:50.253 --> 43:53.588
I would linger until all guests
have departed.

43:53.756 --> 43:57.634
Well, Gaia is a woman
of great appetite.

43:57.802 --> 44:01.179
Dawn will threaten
before she has had her fill.

44:02.932 --> 44:04.641
- Lucretia.
- Hmm?

44:04.809 --> 44:08.687
