absent your light.

44:26.539 --> 44:28.749
See everything restored
to proper place.

44:28.916 --> 44:31.918
- Nothing must be suspected.
- Yes, Domina.

44:33.546 --> 44:36.298
I know you feel it's betrayal.

44:36.466 --> 44:40.302
But there are times
when truth is more hurtful.

44:40.470 --> 44:42.304
Titus must never know.

44:42.472 --> 44:43.930
Domina.

44:50.355 --> 44:52.356
Apollo.

44:52.523 --> 44:54.691
God of the sun.

44:56.444 --> 44:58.195
And truth.

45:01.824 --> 45:05.660
Something often obscured
by the masks we wear.

45:07.914 --> 45:10.332
Your guests have abandoned you.

45:10.500 --> 45:13.293
I thought the toad Solonius
would at least remain.

45:13.461 --> 45:16.546
The hour is late.

45:16.714 --> 45:19.007
He believed you occupied
for the night.

45:19.175 --> 45:21.551
They say Apollo brings warmth
and prosperity

45:21.719 --> 45:23.178
to those who would pray to him.

45:23.346 --> 45:27.307
Those who understand their place
on their knees.

45:28.726 --> 45:30.060
Tullius...

45:30.228 --> 45:32.270
You know, I often dreamt
of Gaia's touch

45:32.438 --> 45:34.731
when I was a younger man.

45:34.899 --> 45:37.234
The taste of her lips.

45:37.402 --> 45:40.862
Now they form words in my ear
asking favor for this house

45:41.030 --> 45:43.323
placing me in difficult position.

45:43.491 --> 45:47.160
Gaia's affections for this house
are genuine.

45:47.328 --> 45:49.621
As are her feelings for you.

45:49.789 --> 45:51.957
Returned in kind.

45:54.001 --> 45:55.961
She holds my reply.

45:56.129 --> 45:59.089
Go to her and see it delivered.

46:15.773 --> 46:17.691
Gaia?

46:18.693 --> 46:20.193
Gaia.

46:43.593 --> 46:46.094
Have you lost mind?

46:46.262 --> 46:48.680
Again attempting to maneuver
around Tullius.

46:48.848 --> 46:51.183
I only sought
to elevate our position.

46:51.350 --> 46:53.852
By plunging the good name
of this house into muck and shit?

46:54.020 --> 46:55.812
What would you have me do?

46:55.980 --> 46:58.315
Bow and scrape
to the fucking lunatic?

46:58.483 --> 47:00.317
He is above our station!

47:00.485 --> 47:02.360
