47:20.296 --> 47:22.964
His life for hers.

47:23.132 --> 47:26.927
Blood and brains
on the fucking floor.

47:27.094 --> 47:29.262
- Reward well deserved.
- No.

47:29.430 --> 47:31.932
There will be no retribution.

47:32.099 --> 47:35.769
- I will see him dead.
- You will do as fucking commanded.

47:39.649 --> 47:41.525
And what of Gaia?

47:46.781 --> 47:48.949
She partook of too much wine...

47:49.992 --> 47:52.494
as she was often known to do.

47:52.662 --> 47:55.205
In the night she lost footing

47:55.373 --> 47:57.666
and fell to her death
at the bottom of the cliff.

47:59.794 --> 48:03.129
Do not look to him.
I am the dominus of this fucking house.

48:03.297 --> 48:05.799
See it done. Quintus.

48:21.691 --> 48:23.858
