something of your own,

48:53.222 --> 48:56.141
something that held meaning to you
even if no one else saw it.

48:56.309 --> 48:58.602
Yet what has she given you?

48:58.769 --> 49:02.647
No dowry to speak of,
no name to elevate status,

49:02.815 --> 49:06.109
and no heir
to carry the name Batiatus.

49:10.406 --> 49:14.826
Every choice you make
shapes your fate, Quintus.

49:14.994 --> 49:17.495
I cannot change
missteps of the past,

49:17.663 --> 49:19.414
but I will see you
on proper path.

49:19.582 --> 49:22.042
And Lucretia
must be swept from it.

49:22.209 --> 49:23.752
You would dissolve my marriage?

49:23.919 --> 49:27.213
No, you will make that choice
for yourself

49:27.381 --> 49:29.591
or be gone from this
house with her.

49:57.662 --> 49:59.496
Wait!
